<body lang="en-US" link="#000080" vlink="#800000" dir="ltr"><h1 class="western">
<font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">OFWONO
GODWIN</font></font></h1>
<h1 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">SEP23/BSE/3344U</font></font></h1>
<p align="center"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt"><b>Selected
Topics In Software Engineering(Test 2)</b></font></font></p>
<h1 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">STUDENT
REGISTRATION SYSTEM</font></font></h1>
<h1 class="western"><br/>
<br/>

</h1>
<h2 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">1.
Introduction</font></font></h2>
<h2 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-weight: normal">This
report documents the improvements made to the Student Registration
System following feedback received from Test 1. The enhancements
focus on three key areas as recommended by the lecturer: </span><b>validation
and error handling, user interface design improvements and additional
features including search, filtering and user authentication.</b></font></font></h2>
<h2 class="western" style="font-weight: normal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">The
improvements transform the basic CRUD application into a
professional, production-ready student management system with modern
design principles and enhanced user experience.</font></font></h2>
<h2 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">2.
Summary of Improvements</font></font></h2>
<p><br/>
<br/>

</p>
<table cellpadding="2" cellspacing="2">
	<tr>
		<th style="border: none; padding: 0in"><p><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Category</font></font></p>
