			Bootstrap styling</font></font></p>
		</td>
		<td style="border: none; padding: 0in"><p><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Professional
			Sunbird AI-inspired design system with custom CSS variables</font></font></p>
		</td>
	</tr>
