<h2 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">3.
New Features Implemented</font></font></h2>
<h3 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">3.1
User Authentication System</font></font></h3>
<p><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">A
complete authentication system was implemented allowing users to
securely access the student management features:</font></font></p>
<ul>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Login
	Page:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Users authenticate using their email address and password with
	&quot;Remember Me&quot; functionality </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Registration
	Page:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	New users can create accounts with full name, email and password </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Secure
	Password Storage:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Passwords are hashed using BCrypt encryption algorithm </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Session
	Management:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Cookie-based authentication with automatic logout on session expiry </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Access
	Control:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Student management pages are protected and require authentication </font></font>
	</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">3.2
Search and Filtering Functionality</font></font></h3>
<p><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Advanced
search capabilities were added to help administrators find students
quickly:</font></font></p>
<ul>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Text
	Search:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Search by student name, registration number, or email address </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Course
	Filter:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Filter students by their enrolled course/program </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Year
	Filter:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Filter by year of study (Year 1 through Year 5) </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Sorting
	Options:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Sort results by name, registration number, course, year, or
	registration date </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Active
	Filter Display:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Visual badges showing currently applied filters with quick clear
	option </font></font>
	</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">3.3
Dashboard Statistics</font></font></h3>
<p><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">The
Students Index page now features real-time statistics cards
displaying:</font></font></p>
<ul>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Total
	number of registered students </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Number
	of students matching current filter criteria </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Count
	of available courses in the system </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Number
	of year levels supported </font></font>
	</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">4.
User Interface Improvements</font></font></h2>
<h3 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">4.1
Design System Implementation</font></font></h3>
<p><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">A
comprehensive design system was created inspired by professional SaaS
applications:</font></font></p>
<ul>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Color
	Palette:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Primary blue (#2563eb), secondary dark (#0f172a) and accent cyan
	(#06b6d4) </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Typography:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Inter font family for modern, readable text across all devices </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">CSS
	Variables:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Centralized design tokens for consistent spacing, shadows and border
	radius </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Responsive
	Design:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Fully responsive layouts that work seamlessly on mobile, tablet and
	desktop </font></font>
	</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">4.2
Navigation and Layout</font></font></h3>
<ul>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Fixed
	Navigation Bar:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Professional navbar with brand logo, centered navigation links and
	user dropdown menu </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Hero
	Section:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Eye-catching landing page with gradient patterns and call-to-action
	buttons </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Professional
	Footer:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Multi-column footer with product links, resources, company
	information and social media icons </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Page
	Headers:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Consistent header sections with gradient backgrounds on all major
	pages </font></font>
	</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">4.3
New Public Pages</font></font></h3>
<ul>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Landing
	Page (Home):</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Marketing-style homepage with hero section, statistics counters,
	feature highlights and call-to-action sections </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">About
	Page:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Information about the system with mission statement and team values </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Features
	Page:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Showcase of system capabilities with icon-based feature cards </font></font>
	</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">4.4
Form and Table Improvements</font></font></h3>
<ul>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Card-Based
	Forms:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Clean form layouts with section titles and organized field groupings
	</font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Enhanced
	Tables:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Hover effects, avatar initials and action button styling </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Empty
	States:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Friendly messages and guidance when no data is available </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Toast
	Notifications:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Success and error messages displayed as dismissible toasts </font></font>
	</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">5.
Enhanced Validation and Error Handling</font></font></h2>
<h3 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">5.1
Student Model Validation</font></font></h3>
<p><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Comprehensive
validation rules were added to the Student entity:</font></font></p>
<ul>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Full
	Name:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Required, 3-100 characters, letters and spaces only </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Email:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Required, valid email format validation </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Registration
	Number:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Required, alphanumeric with slashes pattern (e.g., REG/2024/001) </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Phone
	Number:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Optional, international format validation </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Year
	of Study:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Required, range validation (1-5) </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Course:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Required, 3-100 characters </font></font>
	</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">5.2
User-Friendly Error Messages</font></font></h3>
<ul>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Clear,
	descriptive validation messages displayed inline below each field </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Model-level
	error summary for complex validation failures </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Alert
	banners for authentication errors (invalid credentials, duplicate
	email) </font></font>
	</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">6.
Additional Data Fields</font></font></h2>
<p><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">The
Student model was enhanced with additional fields to capture more
comprehensive student information:</font></font></p>
<ul>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Email
	Address:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	For direct student communication </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Phone
	Number:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Optional contact information </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Date
	of Birth:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	For age verification and records </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Gender:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Male, Female, or Other options </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p style="margin-bottom: 0in"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Created
	At:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Timestamp of student registration </font></font>
	</p></li>
	<li><p><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">Updated
	At:</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">
	Timestamp of last record modification </font></font>
	</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 class="western"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">7.
Conclusion</font></font></h2>
<p><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt">The
improvements implemented in Test 2 have significantly enhanced the
Student Registration System from a basic CRUD application to a
professional, feature-rich management system. The addition of user
authentication ensures data security, while the search and filtering
capabilities improve administrative efficiency. The modern UI design
creates a polished, professional appearance suitable for production
deployment.</font></font></p>
